      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2), a definitive example of high-output, naturally aspirated precision. This vehicle is powered by the F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four, synchronized with a close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis features a rigid X-bone frame and a double-wishbone suspension setup at all four corners, providing surgical steering response and 50:50 weight distribution. This specimen is in flawless condition, retaining all original body panel VIN tags, a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation, and a factory-original soft top with glass rear heating element. Performance is optimized with recent valve clearance adjustments and a full synthetic fluid service. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically perfect, analog masterpiece in showroom state.",
